channelDescription:
Integrity Vision is a Ukrainian IT service company proficient in business automation, integration solutions, financial security, and IT infrastructure for corporate business.

We have 14 years of experience in automating and optimising business processes for corporate business. We have implemented many projects for the financial sector, retail, telecommunications, and public sector, automating such processes as:

🔹 customer identification;
🔹 opening and closing of loans/accounts/deposits;
🔹 credit/debit card delivery;
🔹 new employees onboarding;
🔹 vacation/dismissal/rotation of employees;
🔹 business trips.

Our company has been a partner of Camunda for over 7 years. We have Platinum Partner Certified status and certified developers and implement projects in major banks together with the vendor. KredoBank, Fozzy Group, Vodafone, UKRSIBBANK BNP Paribas Group, Crédit Agricole Bank, and others entrust us with their business processes.

Growth | Efficiency | Trust
